description:
This app shows current Nepali date/time and Nepali Calendar including public holidays, festivals, and other important events. In addition to calendar feature, this app shows current forex values and its trends in last 30 days.  Another important feature is ability to convert nepali date (BS) to Gregorian (Western) calendar (AD) and vice versa.

Celebrate the important days, events and Nepali Festivals with all new e-cards. Share our dashain tihar ecards with your friends and family. 

Now, we are adding "Hamro Radio", one of the best online nepali radio and FM player. 
Explore and watch brand new videos of news, music, tech, sports, entertainment etc  on Hamro Video.
Watch live televisions.

Starting from version 3, we have added ipad support and provided rashifal and gold/silver price trends over last 30 days.

Smart Patro - Nepali Calendar is the Multicultural Nepali Patro with events & festivals of all the cultural ethnic groups of Nepal. It includes public holidays, festivals, panchang and other important events. Smart Patro Nepali Calendar is exclusively developed for iPhone devices with latest development technology to make it much faster and smooth with a quick and clean interface which includes the following basic features useful for the Nepalese community in Nepal and Abroad.

Key Features:
   • Nepali Calendar
   • Date Converter
   • Unit Converter
   • Panchang
   • Rashifal
   • Tithi
   • Suva Sait
   • Reminders
   • Nepali News
   • Nepali FM Radio
   • Nepal Exchange Rates with history graph
   • Gold & Silver Price with a history graph
   • Weather observation Nepal with history graph
   • Videos: Trending videos
   • Calendar Widgets for Homescreen and Lockscreen

Note: Smart Patro always shows the current Nepali Date and Time of Nepal wherever you are in the world.

▶ Nepali Calendar: Nepali calendar with events and festivals of Nepal. The Nepali Calendar also called Nepali Patro uses lunar months and solar sidereal year. It shows both Nepali and English dates with a dot for events or festivals with moon sign for Purnima and Aunsi.
• Double tap on any date to view panchang/tithi for that date
• Long press on any date to set a reminder with Nepali date
• Single tap highlights events/festivals/reminder on the table

▶ Nepali FM: Some of the popular Nepali FM included in this app are Kantipur FM, Hits FM, Kalika FM, Sagarmatha, Ujyaalo 90 Network, Image FM, Radio Nepal, BBC Nepali. Cultural FM likes Newa FM Radio and Nepali News FM.

▶ Forex: Nepali exchange rates and history with the graphical representation available for US Dollar, European Euro, UK Pound Sterling, Australian Dollar, Canadian Dolla, Swiss Franc, Chinese Yuan, Japanese Yen, Saudi Arabian Riyal, Singapore Dollar, Qatari Riyal, Thai Baht, UAE Dirham, Malaysian Ringgit, Bahrain Dinar, Kuwaity Dina, Hong Kong Dollar, Swedish Kroner, South Korean Won, Danish Kron, Indian Rupee.

▶ Date Converter: Nepali Date Converter converts Bikram sambat Nepali date to English date and vice versa for 400+ years. It also shows age different with Panchang (astrological data) for a converted date.

▶ Nepali News: The News section in the app features the latest news articles and trending videos from Nepal. You will no longer have to search the news articles on a lot of different sites just to get single good news for the time being.

▶ Nepali Panchang: It is an astrological value that gives useful astrological information required by an astrologer. With Nepali Panchang, you will get to know various information on Panchang like Tithi, Nakshatra, Yoga, Karana, Vaar, Nepal Sambat, Chandra Rashi, Ritu, Aayan, Sunrise/Sunset and Moonrise/Moonset related information of Nepal for 200+ years. Time is on a 24-hour clock with NST & AV location of Nepal with the precise planetary position.

▶ Reminders: Set reminders in Nepali date. A reminder can be set from Reminders on the menu or by long-pressing on any dates on the Nepali calendar.

▶ Weather: Nepal weather observations for main cities/places with line chart history for Temperature Max℃, Min℃, and Rainfall on a bar graph. Current weather for user location.

DISCLAIMER: We do not claim any ownership rights in any Third-Party Content. All the content available in Nepali Radio, News & Video is the third party content. The contents are free & publicly available to use. Third-Party Content is the property of its respective provider or its licensor.

यो एप्स बनाउनु को मुख्य उदेश्य भनेको वैदिक ज्योतिष सास्त्रलाइ सरल, पहुँचयोग्य, बिश्वासनिय तरीका बाट सम्पुर्ण नेपाली जनमास समक्ष मोबाईल र ईन्टरनेट को माध्यम बाट कुशलतापुर्वक जन्म बिवरण को आधार मा ग्रह, रासी तथा नक्षत्रहरुको स्थिती को सुस्म अध्यन गरि वैदिक ज्योतिषीय नियम लाई पछ्याउदै बैज्ञानिक आधारमा एक असल मार्गदर्शक को भुमिका निर्वाहा गर्ने हो।

तपाईंको सटीक जन्म बिवरण को आधार मा जन्म कुन्डली सहित अन्य वर्ग कुन्डलीहरुको सूक्ष्म अध्ययन गरि स्वास्थ, शिक्षा, पेसा, वैवाहिक जीवन, प्रेम सम्बन्ध, ब्यावसाय आदी बिसय सम्बन्धि परामर्श गर्ने हेतु ले यो एप्स तयार पारीएको हो। ज्योतिष सास्त्र एक आफै मा अत्यन्तै गहन र बृहत ग्यान सागर हो। हामी ले ज्योतिष को माध्यम बाट तपाईं को चलिरहेको सुभ-असुभ समय को आकलन सजिलै गर्न सक्छौ। हामी ले प्रतिकुल समय लाइ Skip गर्दै अनुकुल समय को फाइदा उठाउनु पर्छ।

येदी तपाईं संग आफ्नो जन्म बिवरण केही उपलब्ध छैन भने हामी ले " प्रश्न कुन्डलि" को आधार मा हेर्ने गर्दछौ। यो प्रश्न कुन्डली मा तपाईं ले प्रश्न सोध्नु भएको समय मा आकास मा कता - कता कुन- कुन रासी र नक्षत्र मा ग्रह गोचर थियो सो निर्धारण गरि तेसैको आधार मा फलादेस गरीन्छ। येस्को लागि आवस्यक पर्ने बिवरणहरु यस प्रकार रहेका छन;

1. प्रश्नकर्ता को नाम
2. प्रश्न कर्ता ले प्रश्न सोधेको समय या प्रश्न दिमाग मा जन्म/उदय भएको समय।
3. प्रश्नकर्ता ले कुन ठाउ बाट प्रश्न सोधेको हो उक्त ठाउँ को नाम।
4. प्रश्नकर्ता को प्रश्न।

कसरी प्रयोग गर्ने?

एप्स डाउन्लोड गर्नुस।
आफ्नो ब्याक्तीगत प्रोफाइल बनाउनुहोस।
E-Sewa मा गएर सेवा सुल्क खरीद गर्नुहोस।
आफ्नो प्रश्न राख्नुहोस।
हाम्रो ज्योतिष गुरुहरु बाट उत्तर पाउनुहुनेछ।


यो एप्स मा रासीफल अनि ग्रह गोचरहरुको बारेमा समय-समय मा जानकारी गराइने छ।

आफ्नो जन्म बिवरण हालेर सम्पूर्ण वर्ग कुण्डहरू सजिलै हेर्न सकिन्छ साथै विंशोतरी, योगिनी, त्रिभागि दशा( विं. सं) मा उपलब्ध छ र संगै जन्म सम्पूर्ण जातक विवरण उपलब्ध छ कुनै ज्योतिष बिना सजिलै संग हेर्न सकिन्छ।

- Our members are at the heart of everything we do

Inclusivity is key
At Bumble, we promise to support and include all forms of love: straight, gay, lesbian, queer, and beyond. We want everyone in our community to feel safe and welcome. So no matter how you identify, if you're looking for a place to chat, date, and find real love, we’ve got what you’re looking for.

The DMSS app can enhance your security management efficiency. You can watch real-time surveillance videos and play them back anytime, anywhere, via Wi-Fi or cellular networks. If a device alarm is triggered, DMSS will immediately push an instant notification to you.

DMSS offers：
1. Real-time Live View：
You can view real-time surveillance videos from the added devices anytime, anywhere, to help you better monitor the safety of your home environment.

2. Video Playback：
You can quickly find the events you care about by date and event category, and playback the required historical video footage.

3. Instant Alarm Notifications：
You can subscribe to different alarm events according to your needs.  When an event is triggered, you will immediately receive the message notification.

4. Device Sharing
You can share the device with family members for shared use and assign them different usage permissions.

5. Alarm Hub
You can add a variety of peripheral accessories to the alarm hub to provide warnings for potential theft, intrusion, fire, water damage, and other situations. In case of an unforeseen event, DMSS can immediately activate alarms and send out danger notifications.

6. Visual Intercom
You can add visual intercom devices to engage in video calls between the device and the DMSS, as well as perform functions like locking and unlocking.

7. Access Control
You can add access control devices to check the current status of doors and view unlock records, as well as perform remote unlocking operations on the doors.

Ramro Patro is a Nepali Calendar based application that includes so many features.

Ramro Patro includes Nepali Calendar 2082, 2081, 2080 with festivals like Dashain and Tihar with Tithis, Marriage Dates, Bratabandha dates, Pasni dates, Rudri dates and Hom dates. It also includes calendar for historical years such as 2081, 2080, 2079, 2078, 2077, etc.

It consists of Current Nepali date and Time that shows Nepali date and time at current time along with tithi events for the day, holidays etc.

Nepali Calendar or Ramro Patro consists of so many features such as Nepali date and English date with tithi, panchanga, holidays list, Bibah dates, Bratabandha dates, Hom dates, Pasni Dates, Rudri dates, shortcut menus to festivals such as Dashain, Tihar, New Year, Lhosar, Chaath parba, Maghe sankranti etc.

Nepali Date Converter converts Bikram Sambat date into English Date and English Dates into Bikram sambat date aka BS to AD converter or AD to BS converter.

Nepali Forex shows the current exchange rates of different countries to Nepali Rupees i.e. NPR. It also helps to calculate them.

This app is best considered for Nepali Calendar, Dashain, Tihar, Dashain Tihar Cards, Wallpapers etc.

The recent update includes Nepali Calendar 2082 with festivals like Dashain,Tihar, Events, Panchanga etc for the same year.
